        "勉励。——常用搭配"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "勉"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "赶快",
      "examples": [
        "子之书甚不善，子勉归矣。——《吕氏春秋·具备》"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "勉"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "通“免”。除去，脱掉",
      "examples": [
